The Debian Package vlc-plugin-vlsub
----------------------------

VLsub is a plugin for VLC, the libre and open source media player and 
multimedia engine.
This plugin allows you to automatically download the subtitles for your video,
searching on the website http://opensubtitles.org. The search is based on the
hash of the video currently playing.
The author of the plugin is Guillaume Le Maout, web developer.

Files
----

usr/lib/vlc/lua/extensions/vlsub.lua is the only component of the plugin.

Translations
-----------

Translations of the plugin are downloaded directly from the project github at
https://github.com/exebetche/vlsub/locales/tree/master/locale. In case you wish
to have your own translation, you can add it to your 
~/.local/share/vlc/lua/extensions/locales folder.
The current official available translations are English, Czech, Danish, French,
Greek, Basque, Brazilian Portuguese, Slovak,Spanish, Swedish and Ukrainian

Links
----

